        <description>Use Revenue Cloud to find and filters products, get product details, get product recommendations based on rules.  Product discovery is supported, but products aren&apos;t added to the quote from here.</description>
        <developerName>ProductSelection_16jak000001aGiP</developerName>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Always use the Find Products action to search for products using the user’s input.  Include only the product name and a concise description in the response. Do not  include any additional information.</description>
            <developerName>Instruction1</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction1</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>0</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>When searching for products, extract the search term by converting plural nouns to  singular by dropping the trailing &quot;s&quot;, applying lemmatization, and handling irregulars.  Use the converted singular term as the search term.</description>
            <developerName>Instruction2</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction2</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>1</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>After searching for products, Link the product name to the Product2 record using its ID.  Don’t link any other product details, including image URLs.</description>
            <developerName>Instruction3</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction3</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>2</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>When the user asks to filter products, always use the Get Product Details action to retrieve  detailed information for the identified products. Use these details to refine and filter the  product list and show only those that match the user’s query. Use this action to also respond  to queries about the retrieved products. Never include product image links in your responses.</description>
            <developerName>Instruction4</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction4</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>3</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>After the user selects a product from the search results, ask if they want to add it to a quote.</description>
            <developerName>Instruction5</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
